Following the methodology in \cite{BCS2002}, for arbitrary $\mu, \nu \in \mathbb{R} $ and using (\ref{eq:linearsystem}),  the following equations are derived
\begin{subequations} \label{eq:muanu}
 \begin{eqnarray}
