\tilde{u}^{\theta }_{\tilde{t }\tilde{x}\tilde{x}}=(1-\nu ) \tilde{u}^{\theta }_{\tilde{t }\tilde{x}\tilde{x}}-\nu{\tilde{\eta }}_{\tilde{x}\tilde{x}\tilde{x}}+\mathcal{O}(\alpha, \beta) 
